Class StreamsClientImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.symphonyoss.symphony.clients.impl.StreamsClientImpl

    StreamsClient

    public class StreamsClientImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements StreamsClient
    Supports all stream lookup and create functions. This also includes ability to search and updates for rooms.
